data.description: Beautiful, Welcoming Entry!  Enormous Garage with Heater!  Luxury Cabana-Styled Covered 13' X 26' Patio with Ceiling Fans!  Finished Basement with Large Bedroom, Full Bathroom, and Incredible Storage Space!  A must see!  Every inch of this home has been loved and treated with care!  Immaculate!  Electric and Gas hook up for Oven/Stove, High Impact Owens Corning Roof Shingles, European Oak Engineered Hardwood Flooring, Edgewood Carpet with 8lb density 1/2" Pad, Vaulted Ceiling, High-End Cabinetry throughout, Large Walk-In Master Closet with adjustable racks and shelving, and more!  Don't wait, this one will not last!
